official_title: A resolution authorizing the printing of additional copies of the report entitled "Development in Aging: 1972 and January-March 1973".

summary.text: Provides that there be printed for the use of the Special Committee on Aging one thousand eight hundred additional copies of its report to the Senate entitled "Developments in Aging: 1972 and January-March 1973".
